<Class name="CM_CashInvoiceProformaAgent" id="c6c55225-bd27-4530-896b-fcb11ac8a8ce">
    <superclass name="CM_Agent"/>
    <transient/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <DbClassMap file="proForma"/>
    <ImplicitInverseRef name="allCashPayments" id="6d50f47d-101b-4fd3-8c4d-f1d628576397">
        <memberTypeInverse/>
        <type name="CM_CashPaymentDict"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>All persistent cash payments for this cargo item.</text>
    </ImplicitInverseRef>
    <ImplicitInverseRef name="allChildAgents" id="e8909c42-ccba-48ae-a327-d5bc1fa829d5">
        <memberTypeInverse/>
        <type name="ObjectArray"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>

DELETE NO LONGER USED</text>
    </ImplicitInverseRef>
    <ImplicitInverseRef name="allCurrentInvLines" id="5650874a-149c-4422-bd29-68c93113cdc5">
        <memberTypeInverse/>
        <type name="CM_InvoiceLineSet"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>All invoice lines for a cash-only debtor from the cargo item.
See selectedInvoiced for the matching cash collection selection of these lines.</text>
    </ImplicitInverseRef>
    <ImplicitInverseRef name="allOwingInvoicedLines" id="16d10b70-1bbc-4920-8e94-b86e847a660b">
        <memberTypeInverse/>
        <type name="CM_InvoiceLineSet"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>
PELINDO1 WORK ORDER CASH ONLY

In April 2018 I discovered that the cash collection screen does not handle actual invoice lines that are part paid.
E.g. a proforma invoice line is paid for a quantity of 2 when the actual invoice line is created it has an invoice line of 4.

This was discovered testing voyage cash.

In cargo cash this difference between proforma payments are handled, the actual invoic elines for these cargo under payments are 
typically for storage. Storage only gets an actual invoice line when the cargo is released.

So I added this collection to hold the transient invoice lines that represent the unpaid portion.</text>
    </ImplicitInverseRef>
    <ImplicitInverseRef name="allProformaCriteria" id="4953712d-7513-4097-bdc5-dd656fef75cd">
        <memberTypeInverse/>
        <type name="CM_ProformCritByBankByPriority"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>A copy of myBank.allProformaCriteria used to find the configured transactions for the pro forma invoice lines.</text>
    </ImplicitInverseRef>
    <ImplicitInverseRef name="allProformaInvLines" id="aaac672b-14df-4151-b03c-cd5b7aa391f9">
        <memberTypeInverse/>
        <type name="CM_InvoiceLineSet"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>All pro forma invoice lines (transient copies of the real ones) from the configured transaction types.
These are the expected extra charges due when the cargo is released (imports) or shipped (exports).
See selectedEstimated for the matching cash collection selection of these lines.</text>
    </ImplicitInverseRef>
