        <text>The sum of the allProformaInvLines value, the extra amount over the current charges which is due for payment.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
    <PrimAttribute name="ignoreCurrentInvoiceLines" id="093679a4-6b29-4193-809f-74a471cfd084">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Boolean"/>
    </PrimAttribute>
    <PrimAttribute name="ignoreProformaForRoadRelease" id="d96d7699-c218-44c3-9126-2feb6d462b3c">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Boolean"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>


This boolean is set from the cash collection 'For Cargo Release'.
Depending on whether the cargo is import or export and depending on whether it is on ship or on site, it includes all the basic transaction types.

e.g. for import it adds receive ship, release road and storage. If it is a reefer it also adds Reefer Daily.

It is possible to not configure any proforma transactions and just use this option.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
    <PrimAttribute name="invoicedCashCharges" id="5e957342-00b0-4304-b48a-0b54fdab9aee">
        <precision>23</precision>
        <scaleFactor>6</scaleFactor>
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Decimal"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>The sum of the allCurrentInvLines invoice lines, the amount which has already been charged.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
